<h2>Growth and Future Projections</h2>
<p><strong>39. Ecommerce is projected to reach $7.89 trillion by 2028.</strong>
(Source: Statista, 2026)
The 5-year outlook shows consistent 7-8% annual growth. No single market disruption is expected to change this trajectory.</p>
<p><strong>40. By 2027, ecommerce will represent 23%+ of total retail sales.</strong>
(Source: Statista, 2026)
For context, ecommerce was 14% of retail in 2019. The pandemic accelerated online adoption by 3-5 years.</p>
